HEADWORD: Alarming
<hw>A*larm"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Exciting, or calculated to
excite, alarm; causing apprehension of danger; <as>as, an
<ex>alarming</ex> crisis or report</as>. -- A*larm"ing*ly,
<xex>adv</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

